  "intent": "Execute anti-CD154 immunolabeling protocol on peptide- and PMA-stimulated cells across multiple test columns. Add 5\u00b5L anti-CD154 antibody to 200\u00b5L cell suspensions in row A wells with mixing. Distribute 40\u00b5L aliquots to rows B-E, supplementing with 60\u00b5L culture medium per well. Stimulate with 5\u00b5L peptide 1 (row B), 5\u00b5L peptide 2 (row C), 10\u00b5L peptide 3 (row D), and 12\u00b5L PMA/calcium ionophore (row E), mixing after each addition.",
